text: Collège français Jules-Verne is a French international school in Ciudad del Este, Paraguay. It serves levels primaire (primary school) through lycée (senior high school/sixth form college). Collège (junior high school) and lycée students use the National Centre for Distance Education (CNED) distance education programme."A propos de nous... " Collège français Jules-Verne. Retrieved on September 2, 2016. Preschool and elementary school are directly taught. The school was established in 2008."Collège Français Jules Verne de Ciudad del Este ." Embassy of France in Paraguay.
